ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAGREEMENT - Bring into force Turks and Caicos Islands FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of TURKS AND CAICOS ISLANDS under entrustment from the Government of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS, signed in the Turks and Caicos Islands on 22 June 2010.
